description: Newspaper published in Portland, Oregon, United States
label: Business Tribune
title: Business_Tribune
exrest: The Business Tribune is a trade newspaper in Portland, Oregon, established in 2014 and published twice a week, on Tuesdays and Fridays. The Business Tribune website is updated daily and breaking news bulletins are posted on topics including business, development, legal news and public notices, mainly in the Portland metro area. It is locally-owned and readership reaches state-wide.
